Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, we're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So everypony got an urgent\Nsummons to the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with no explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I just love a good\Nmysterious summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it about? Do you\Nthink it's a surprise party?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are we running?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because something could\Nbe terribly wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony turned bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,another evil creature\Nback for revenge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're\Nbeing a little paranoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would the princesses\Nsend scrolls in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. They'd know\Nbetter than to make us worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I like it when\Nyou run so fast;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the walls get all blurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheee!\NRace ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, thank you\Nso much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!? What can we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it. Nothing's\Nwrong. Everything's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did y'all call us down\Nhere just to tell us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due\Nrespect, Majesties,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you might want to save\Nyour urgent summons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for matters that are a\Nbit more... well, urgent?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria is currently\Nenjoying its longest period
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of harmony in recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all thanks\Nto you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And your\Nfriends, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pshaw! [giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time\Nyou noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been less\Nand less for us to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after much consideration,\Nmy sister and I have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it is time for us... to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking News! The royal\Nprincesses retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many\Nquestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll take over? Who\Nwill run Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be someone\Ntall, dark, and handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or will it be the\NLord of Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine, go with\Nthe obvious choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're retiring!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Princesses can retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we can! I, for\None, am looking forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to a little R&R, maybe\Na trip to Silver Shoals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want {\i1}me{\i0} to\Ntake your place!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With the help of your\Nfriends, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't think of\Nanypony more worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the years, we've\Nwatched you grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've faced\Ntask after task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...challenge\Nafter challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...countless adversities. Yeah,\Nyeah, we get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've always\Nprevailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but that\Ndoesn't mean that I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that {\i1}we're{\i0} ready\Nto do what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Of course you are. I realize\Nthis is a lot to take in, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Makes perfect\Nsense. We're awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Does this mean we\Nget all your powers!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo-oo! I call dibs on showing\Nup in everypony's dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be ready to step\Ninto their horse shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if the Princesses\Nthink it's time to retire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not a bad choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We always have Equestria's\Nbest interests at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fair point,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which should be taken\Ninto consideration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,when we have a\Nroundtable discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Darlings! We'll all need a\Ncomplete wardrobe update.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would love to pick your\Nbrain about mane maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we all have each\Nother, I'm sure we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Protectors of Equestria\Non three. One, two--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're all on board,\NI guess I am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Protectors of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a bit of\Nan adjustment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I imagine the\Ntransfer of power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will be a lengthy process\Nwhich will give me--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we just\Nneed a few days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to put together a\Nlittle ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. A few DAYS!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't there be some\Nsort of training program?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That lasts weeks, no,\Nmonths, if not YEARS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you've gone\Nthrough over the years
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,has been a\Ntraining program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, but there's got to be\Na guide or a rule book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have it right here:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to Rule Equestria"\Nby Nopony McPretendsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Friendship Journal\Nyou wrote yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is a better guide than\Nany we could provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the utmost\Nconfidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hope you have\Nthe same in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm absolutely\Ncertain she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not confident\Nabout this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I thought.\NI was being sarcastic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is all\Nso predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the part where you all\Ntell little Sparkle here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything is\Ngoing to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But she won't believe you.\N[groan] I don't need to be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I know I said\Nyes, but then they said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"in a few days" and there's\Nstill so much to figure out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all happening so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I need some--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulp] OK. I'll feel\Nmuch better--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you make\Na plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Wow. It's\Nlike you--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--knew you were going to\Nreact this way? We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Classic Twilighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Twilighting?" You...\Nyou made me a verb?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad thing, we just\Nknow you have a.... process.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage one. You get big\Nnews, and you're like "No!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you pace, and\Nyou chart, you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. You go\Nahead and "Twilight"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all acting so calm,\Nbut this is a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do if\Nsomething big happens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the princesses\Naren't there to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... If you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they literally\Nalmost never help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. we still always win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when Sombra almost took\Nback the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or when Chrysalis\Npretended to be Cadance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or when Tirek came back and\Nabsorbed all the magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or the other time Chrysalis\Ntried to take over,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or with Cozy Glow and the\Nschool. [gasp] Am I missing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony of Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight when\Nshe was evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord when he was evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do Flim and\NFlam count?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We've almost\Nalways done things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without the princesses' help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which makes sense now because\Nit was all just training
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it worked. I mean,\Nif you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,there hasn't been\Na single villain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that we couldn't defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat Twilight\NSparkle and her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will pay for\Nstealing my kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pssst! Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is {\i1}Lord{\i0} Tirek\Nand what is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to make\Nsure you can see my
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"best friends rock\Nsculpture" from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A changeling?\NSee? She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis, Queen\Nof the Changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at least I will be when I'm\Nrestored to my rightful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you summon\Nme? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Oh, golly! We\Ndidn't bring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you freed\Nus from Tartarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tartarus? Whoever\Npulled you from there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,must have been somepony\Nvery powerful, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra! You\Nhave returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you\Nbring us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep voice: He didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You may call me... Grogar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The{\i0} Grogar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you\Nwere a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who..?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you, I\Nam very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have all been brought\Nhere as part of my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to rid Equestria of Twilight\NSparkle and her friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry, but\Nthe name Grofar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,just doesn't\Nring any bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,GROGAR! I have\Nbeen away too long
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if my name no longer\Nstrikes fear into the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of one so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a demonstration\Nof power is in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Grogar is ancient and\Nextremely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The land that would\Nbecome Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was a mere collection\Nof farms and pastures
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,until he declared himself\NEmperor of all he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing tales of\Nhis tyranny when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have also heard of the\Nfirst Emperor of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the "Father of Monsters."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave life to the\Nfoulest of creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowed them to run wild,\Ntaking what they wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroying the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My reign was a glorious\Nfear-soaked epoch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of darkness in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Until Gusty the Great\Nrose up and banished you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool believed taking\Nmy bell would defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but she only weakened\Nme temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Tirek is {\i1}really{\i0} old. No\Noffense, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he knew about\Nyou when he was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we have super-different ideas\Nabout what "temporarily" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! I have spent\Nmillennia gathering power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,biding my time, waiting\Nfor the perfect opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to seize control of Equestria!\NAnd watching all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen each of your\Nhumiliating defeats
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hooves of\Nsix puny ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you know why\Nthey've always bested you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are\Nannoyingly lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a kid, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because they\Nwork together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where one is weak, another\Nis strong and thus unified,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,they are a formidable force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we shall use their own\Nstrategy to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest nothing. I\NDEMAND that you join me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and together Equestria\Nwill be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do "ours",\NI only do MINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take back the\NCrystal Empire on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will destroy anypony\Nwho gets in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Such confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Try to take\Nback your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall send you\Nthere myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you prevail, you\Nmay keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you fail,\Nyou will submit to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I refuse this... deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall return\Nyou to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from which you\Nwere summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. But this is\Na waste of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as I will crush\Nthose who defy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat all who\Nget in my way. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I advise the rest of you to\Nprepare to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, working together\Nsounds an awful lot like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,making friends, so\Nyou two are in luck
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know all\Nabout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Twi? You in here? With the\Nschool closed for the summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think anypony\Nwould be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So much to do, not enough\Ntime. No! I already did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Nope. I didn't.\NOOOH, NOT ENOUGH TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP! She's spiraling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the "my plan\Nneeds a plan" stage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Total Twilight\NMelt Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I write down "eliminate\Nredundant lists"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on my School of\NFriendship to-do list,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,or my personal to-do list?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,TWILIGHT!           Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight! Oh, good, you're\Nhere. I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, I had "talk to\NStarlight" written down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on one of these. Just let me\Nfind it so I can cross it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you are\N"Twilighting" hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You say\NTwilighting too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, EXCUSE me, but\Nthis is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ever been asked\Nto run A WHOLE KINGDOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right. You're right... Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So.. what did you want\Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Here it is. I\Nwrote it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, you have blossomed\Ninto one of the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,smartest, most\Ncaring ponies I know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't think of anypony\Nbetter to leave in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of my castle and the\NSchool of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT? You want ME to\Ntake care of the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and RUN THE SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can't! I'm\Nnot ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what happened\Nthe last time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you left me in charge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you want me\Nto do it PERMANENTLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I don't do the\Nright things!? [gasping] What if--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight! Get a\Nhold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've risen to every\Nchallenge you've ever faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do anything you put\Nyour mind to. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! And so do you!\NSee what I did there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said everything\NYOU need to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Nice try, but running\Na school and running a country
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are two very different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you don't\Nmind, I have 7,432
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,more things to take\Ncare of before I become
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the new Ruler of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a valiant effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The guard says Sombra's\Nbreached the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Twilight! We need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have\NFlurry Heart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought\Nyou had her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[whining] Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get\Naway with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I\Nalready have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Cyrstal heart\Nnow in my possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to\Nstop me from ruling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel before Sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Long live the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, but if you're\Ngoing to be the ruler
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of Equestria, you may want\Nto work on your penmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cadance sent an\Nemergency message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra's back and he's taking\Nover the Crystal Empire."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what it says!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But how is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Crystal\NHeart had dispelled him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,into the Ether!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea, but he's\Nback and it's up to us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to save the Empire\Nand my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't somepony\Ntell Celestia and Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One of us should probably\Nloop in the {\i1}real{\i0} rulers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If we're going\Nto run Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need to handle things\Nlike this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight! Could\Nthis mean that you finally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,have the confidence to\Nascend to the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,like the princesses\Nbelieve you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... Unless you'd consider\Ntaking care of Sombra for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no no no no no. You\Nwere absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to learn how to handle\Nthese things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-tah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Handling things on our\Nown is all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but last time we defeated\NSombra with the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he has it already?\NHow are we gonna stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With those, we can defeat\Nanypony, even Sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah no no no no.\NYou didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the "Elements" the last\Ntime you defeated Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure using\Nthem still counts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as handling things\Non your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My family is in danger.\NI'm not taking any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, can you stay here\Nand take care of the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute that you think\Nthat will do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not, but they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cavalry's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] How can I be surprised\Nwhen I'm waiting to show
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you your greatest fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight. How\Ndisappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria was in your care\Nand you let it be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can defeat\Nyour own fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't need to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We just needed to face them\Nlong enough to distract you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute that you think\Nthat will do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have won the battle,\Nbut I shall win the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya hoo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We totally just wiped\Nthe castle with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As magical battles go,\Nthat was a cakewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm, "cakewalk".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We did handle this\Npretty well.. on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't feel like I'm\None hundred percent ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but will I ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you? Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you guys, and we have\Nthe Elements, and together,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we've never failed.\NWe'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, Equestria is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we\Ndo to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I vote for a cakewalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
